---
title: Spiced Shepherd's Pie with Tenderstem Broccoli
description: We've put a twist on an old favourite with today's recipe by adding a hint of Middle Eastern-style spice to a traditional shepherd's pie. We're also leaving the skins on the potatoes for the mash. It's not just out of laziness either - they're full of nutrients and fibre? So, less work and more goodness. Double win!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/spiced-shepherd-s-pie-ff9041fa.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/spiced-shepherd-s-pie-77e00c41.pdf
author: HelloFresh
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipes/spiced-shepherd-s-pie-594156e8c6243b295e79a042
servings: 2
cuisine: Middle Eastern
course: main course
time required: 40 minutes
